SUMMARY:Azure Decoded: Kickstart AI Security with Microsoft Defender for Cloud
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nStart your journey to secure AI workloads in the cloud. Learn how Defender for Cloud provides foundational protection for your AI solutions and why it’s essential for modern security strategies.\n\n**What you’ll learn:**\n- Identify the layers that make up AI workloads in Azure\n- Recognize security risks unique to AI\, including prompt injection\, data leakage\, and model misuse\n- Explain how Microsoft Foundry provides guardrails and observability for AI models\n- Describe how Microsoft Defender for Cloud\, Microsoft Purview\, and Microsoft Entra ID work together to secure and govern AI workloads\n- Summarize how these services align to create a unified\, defense-in-depth strategy for AI security in Azure\n\n**Who should attend:** Developers\, Security Engineers\, and technical professionals who want to learn how Defender for Cloud provides foundational protection for AI solutions and why it’s essential for modern security strategies.\n\n-------------------------------------------------------\n[Enable threat protection for AI services](https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/defender-for-cloud/ai-onboarding/?wt.mc_id=meetup_26842_webpage_reactor)\n[Defender for Cloud - AI threat protection](https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/defender-for-cloud/ai-threat-protection/?wt.mc_id=meetup_26842_webpage_reactor)\n\n📌 This session is a part of a series! Learn more [**here**](https://developer.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1644/?wt.mc_id=meetup_S-1644_webpage_reactor)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/microsoft-reactor-toronto/events/313404622/
